snippet.title: Starship Eleven Deluxe
snippet.description: Starship Eleven Deluxe Sequel to Starship Seven. Explore over 30 strange worlds.

snippet.title: Death vs Monstars
snippet.description: Death vs Monstars Action shooter. Kill all the monstars, collect the coins, buy insane upgrades and kill the end boss!

snippet.title: Doodle Dino Bowl
snippet.description: Doodle Dino Bowl Let the bowling ball fly as far as possible. Collect the stars and pins to buy upgrades in the shop.

snippet.title: Starship Seven
snippet.description: Starship Seven Fly around your UFO in this cave like cavern shoot missiles and destroy enemies.

snippet.title: Little Stars: Players Pack
snippet.description: Little Stars: Players Pack Use your troops to attack enemy stars and try to conquer the entire network.

snippet.title: Fill The Sky With Stars
snippet.description: Fill The Sky With Stars Keep your star up in the sky for as long as you can by hitting stars and clouds.

snippet.title: Ghosted
snippet.description: Ghosted Puzzle game. Help the ghost to pick up all stars and reach the exit of each challenging level.

snippet.title: Death vs Monstars 2
snippet.description: Death vs Monstars 2 Arcade shooter. Play the Death and kill all the monsters. Collect the coins to upgrade your weapons.

snippet.title: Demon Destroyer
snippet.description: Demon Destroyer Use the tadpoles to throw all the demons from the platform. Catch the stars for extra points.

snippet.title: Tofu Ninja
snippet.description: Tofu Ninja Platform game. As a brand new ninja you must collect all stars and make sure to reach your destiny.
